{"tid":1614885,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2019區議會選舉提名攻略","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:25:37.000Z","uid":77642,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98ce3a4626e858fcbdffadd76611b0e1def54690","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:25:05.000Z","msg":"十月四號開始就係區議會選舉提名期。<br />\n可能有好多新手參加區議會選舉，無咩參選經驗，亦都未必有人教路，<br />\n今日呢個post就大約講下提名期要交D咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太過文字性既野，例如選民、候選人資格，定義上既野就唔多講，<br />\n可以直接睇「選舉活動指引」，下面係電子版既link<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/dc_guide.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2Fdc_guide.htm&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7LPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=75c8564a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/dc_guide.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n今次呢個post係想講提名期你要做咩，要交咩表，D表點填，同埋要帶咩去參選。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一。表格下載<br />\n提名相關既表格大多數可以係網上下載，除左「方格表」之外，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">「方格表」一定要係民政或者選舉事務處拎。</span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他表格下載網址如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_candidates_form.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2019dc_candidates_form.htm&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7LPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=bf7f350f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_candidates_form.htm</a><br />\n之後就每份表講下點填。<br />\n<br />\n二。提名表格<br />\n頭一版既個人資料最好跟番身份證照抄，特別係英文名可以用大楷。<br />\n第二版，英文住址唔好用縮寫，通訊地址唔填就會當同住址一樣。<br />\n職業同公司可以唔填，但職業同住址會放上政府憲報比公眾睇(好似係)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二版最底有個提供予公眾人仕查閱資料，係咩黎呢?<br />\n就係因為公眾係可以查閱提名表格，只係佢地查閱既版本會遮左個人資料，<br />\n所以就有呢個位既出現，如果你想比人公眾睇到聯絡資料就填啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三四版係提名人資料，只要十個有效提名就夠，最緊要既係：<br />\n1. 提名人資料要同身份證完全相同，如果唔係就會由選舉主任裁定是否有效。<br />\n2. 如果有任何更改，就要由相關提名人係更改旁邊簽名作實，否則未必會被接受。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第五六版係候選人聲明部分，簽名就OK，<br />\n第七版係指有一個見證人見證住候選人填第五六版。<br />\n重點1：一定要填好晒五六七版先好交表<br />\n重點2：第二部分有咩更改最好有見證人簽署<br />\n重點3：第七版日期唔可以早過第六版，最好一樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就係交選舉按金，選舉按金要$3000，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最好就比現金</span></span>，選舉按金係拎得番既，如果：<br />\n在 下 列 情 況 下 ， 按 金 會 退 回 候 選 人 ：<br />\n(a) 候 選 人 未 獲 有 效 提 名 ；<br />\n(b) 候 選 人 退 出 競 選 ；<br />\n(c) 在確定 某候選人獲有效提名參加選舉之後， 及 在指明舉行選舉的日期前， 候選人已去世或喪失獲提 名 資 格 ； <br />\n(d) 選 舉 被 終 止 ；<br />\n(e) 候 選 人 在 選 舉 中 當 選 ； 或<br />\n(f ) 候選人所得的選票不少於選舉中有效選票總和的5%。 <br />\n交完會有張收據，一定要袋好，拎番錢就靠佢。<br />\n<br />\n一陣再講埋其他表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7dff5b735021f2536d35083a6368a0b8a8d76f4","tid":1614885,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"PISHHHHHHH"},{"pid":"4250f752494b59e0957fe3ef4f0de42651588607","tid":1614885,"uid":54086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1963208f15e7d9817d986c612e7473ea3978d2f7","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"三。方格表<br />\n方格表係用黎做候選人簡介，上面既所有資料都會比公眾睇到。<br />\n唔係必需要交，但交左一定有著數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點：<br />\n1. 一定要有兩張彩色近照，去到現場先貼方格表附有既label又得，貼定先都得。<br />\n2. 方格一定要親身拎。<br />\n3.唔可以scan完係電腦打再print一定要手寫、貼上、打印上方格表而唔可以破壞原有格式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.選舉訊息有誤導性陳述係犯法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.如果候選人係選舉訊息表示得到某人/某組織既支持，一定要交支持同意書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人名義支持同意書：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12a_dc(2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2F2019dce%2Freo_c12a_dc%282019&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7LPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=781211a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12a_dc(2019</a>).pdf<br />\n組織名義支持同意書：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12b_dc(2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2F2019dce%2Freo_c12b_dc%282019&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7LPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=51ed670f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12b_dc(2019</a>).pdf<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b66ed0b04ac43111ad491fd2c19ca3844ae5ce","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"四。提出於選票上印上關於候選人的詳情的請求(BP7)<br />\n呢個如果係素人既話，真係無咩要填<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為呢張野係用黎係選票上面加標誌，最多加三個<br />\n而呢D標誌要一早已經登記，即係D咩咩聯會，或者政黨之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n素人淨係可以加獨立候選人同自己張相。<br />\n交表既時候記得帶一張彩色近照<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係想加訂明團體既名同相，就要填「訂明團體......同意書」(BP9)<br />\n拎提名表既時候會有埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7d9417a6454e40bb1c63f80f9fcd000a7781fb","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"五。在指定展示位置展示選舉廣告的意願書<br />\n唔好比指定展示位置個名嚇親，其實即係街邊banner位同屋邨poster位，<br />\n唔係必定要交，但唔交就會當你放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好蝕底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2769ca02237f476bfe2f50222f67a4d4d48aae9","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"六。確認書<br />\n呢份野唔係提名表格既一部分，無話一定要交先可以參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係幫助RO決定你係咪愛國愛港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而法例上，選舉主任係有權咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果想真係有得選，可以交埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16743af60be43b3dbcbc37ff85edb94512a69b6","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"如果各位有問題都可以係到問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e4938f1f5427390e4057157aa687ecb1d1e995","tid":1614885,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1963208f15e7d9817d986c612e7473ea3978d2f7","tid":1614885,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"三。方格表<br />\n方格表係用黎做候選人簡介，上面既所有資料都會比公眾睇到。<br />\n唔係必需要交，但交左一定有著數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點：<br />\n1. 一定要有兩張彩色近照，去到現場先貼方格表附有既label又得，貼定先都得。<br />\n2. 方格一定要親身拎。<br />\n3.唔可以scan完係電腦打再print一定要手寫、貼上、打印上方格表而唔可以破壞原有格式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.選舉訊息有誤導性陳述係犯法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.如果候選人係選舉訊息表示得到某人/某組織既支持，一定要交支持同意書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人名義支持同意書：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12a_dc(2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2F2019dce%2Freo_c12a_dc%282019&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7LPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=781211a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12a_dc(2019</a>).pdf<br />\n組織名義支持同意書：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12b_dc(2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2F2019dce%2Freo_c12b_dc%282019&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7LPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=51ed670f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dce/reo_c12b_dc(2019</a>).pdf<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55024ea1775c90ee537b1c5606baa1d44e6a1859","tid":1614885,"uid":36642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46e4938f1f542